<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5028446>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Epigyne and endogyne of Eutittha mordax (L. Koch, 1866) and E. insulana Thorell, 1878. a. E. mordax epigyne, ventral view. b. E. insulana endogyne, dorsal view. Abbreviations: AR – anterior rim; CD – copulatory duct; S – spermathecae. Scale bar: g 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5028446/files/figure.png" .

